{"id":1229,"date":"2025-04-12T00:06:10","date_gmt":"2025-04-11T17:06:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1229"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:38:25","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:38:25","slug":"seo-long-chao-day-hop","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/seo-long-chao-day-hop\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u1eb9o l\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3o, \u0111\u00e1y h\u1ed9p"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho s\u1eb9o rolling scar v\u00e0 boxcar scar<\/em><\/p>\n<h3>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111au kh\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, kh\u00f4ng t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ecb s\u1eb9o l\u00f5n, s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1edbi 95%<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng b\u00f3c t\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1y s\u1eb9o b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kim y khoa v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e2m xuy\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u1eb9o \u0111\u00e3 x\u01a1 c\u1ee9ng, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Laser Fractional Co2 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tia Laser Co2 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng 10.600nm t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1edbp h\u1ea1 b\u00ec da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng xung quanh.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da s\u1eb9o t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng( tu\u1ef3 thu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb9o)<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n t\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1y s\u1eb9o kho\u1ea3ng 30 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho s\u1eb9o rolling scar v\u00e0 boxcar scar<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3665,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[40],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1229","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-seo","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1229","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1229"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3665"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1229"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1229"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=1229"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=1229"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}